(2094, 1, '2018-08-23 08:39:06', '2018-08-23 08:39:06', '[vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text][wpdatachart id=1][/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]The above table demonstrates the returns generates by the Vega strategy on a live account comprising the Founder\'s capital.\r\n\r\nThe Vega Fund is an open-ended unit trust with a minimum initial investment of $100,000. The investment class is such that this strategy is only suitable for sophisticated investors.\r\n\r\nEstablished in April 2018, The Vega Fund aims to achieve high absolute returns over the long run through investment in a portfolio of derivative assets.\r\n\r\nUsing our proprietary applications, we at Vega Capital run an algorithm which produces daily valuations on more than 50,000 options trading over various market indices such as the S&amp;P500, the Dow Jones Industrial average and the NASDAQ.\r\n\r\nFrom this screen, a portfolio is created from the most mis-priced options. This portfolio is then tailored to be in sync with the current business.\r\n\r\nOur algorithms monitor the economy and financial markets on a monthly basis to maximise the upside and minimise downside risks. Finally we build a hedging portfolio from other options and futures to remove excessive levels of risk.\r\n\r\nSuch an approach has historically produced high absolute returns on a long term basis.\r\n\r\nTo invest in the Vega Fund, please click the \'Invest in Vega\' link to download and complete our application form. You can download our Information Memorandum within the same link.\r\n\r\n<i>Historical results have certain inherent limitations and hence may not represent actual future realised performance and should not be interpreted as a guarantee of future performance.</i>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Performance', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '2045-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-08-23 08:39:06', '2018-08-23 08:39:06', '', 2045, 'http://vegacapital.net/new/uncategorized/2045-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 