turns are pre-fee and do not include tax.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-84eaeb0 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"84eaeb0\" data-element_type=\"text-editor.default\">\r\n<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\r\n<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\r\n\r\n<em>“You get recessions, you have stock market declines. If you don’t understand that’s going to happen, then you’re not ready, you won’t do well in the markets.” – Peter Lynch</em>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_single_image image=\"2108\" img_size=\"full\"][vc_single_image image=\"2109\" img_size=\"full\"][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'our philosophy', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'our-philosophy', '', '', '2018-08-23 09:44:02', '2018-08-23 09:44:02', '', 0, 'http://vegacapital.net/new/?page_id=2103', 0, 'page', '', 0),
