(2780, 1, '2018-08-23 11:11:26', '2018-08-23 11:11:26', '&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\nMemo to: Vega Capital clients\r\nFrom: Scott Shuttleworth\r\nSubject: Performance update\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<em>Neither the information, nor any opinion, contained on this Website constitutes a solicitation or offer by Vega Capital Pty Ltd (“Vega Capital”) or its affiliates to buy or sell any securities, futures, options or other financial instruments. Decisions based on information contained on this Website are the sole responsibility of the visitor whom we would encourage to seek relevant advice from a licenced professional.</em>\r\n\r\nOver the past few days, I\'ve has been meeting with various institutions and investors who have been enquiring about investing in the Vega fund. As part of these discussions, I was asked to put together a small graph of our live returns versus a handful of competitors who have a similar focus on absolute returns.\r\n\r\nThe results of this are below - Vega has generated a 7 per cent return since inception and is well above many peers.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"size-full wp-image-2716 aligncenter\" src=\"https://vegacapital.net/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/vegaperf.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"650\" height=\"431\" />\r\n\r\nI am delighted that Vega has managed to perform well. That said, it\'s early days and I continue to be focused on the next year or two as opposed to anything more short term.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nThe Vega Fund has now formally launched and is open to sophisticated and wholesale investors. Qualified investors may find our Information Memorandum and Application Form <a href=\"https://vegacapital.net/invest/\">here</a> however if you would like a hard copy mailed to you, please don’t hesitate to contact our office on 1800 960 707.\r\n\r\n<em>Vega Capital is a Corporate Authorised Representative (No. 001264482) of Alpha Securities Pty Ltd (ACN 124 327 064) AFS Licence No. 330757.</em>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Performance update', '', 'inherit', 'closed'